Is G@G a homo conspiracy?

Guy__
Xper 7 Age: 24


In gematria, g@g reduces to 5. Because G=7, it is the 7th letter.

Symbols such as @ don't count.

G@G = 7+7=14.

14 = 1+4=5.

If you count every 5th letter of GirlsAskguYs you get GAY.
